#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 7. Diddhasutta → diddhavisallasuttaṃ (bj) | diṭṭhaṃ (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Diddhasutta"
msgstr "7. A Poisoned Arrow"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.230"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.7:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

#. VAR: diddhagatena visallena sallena → diṭṭhigatena visallena (si) | diṭṭhigatena sallena (s1-3, km) | diṭṭhagatena visallena sallena (pts1-2) | diṭṭhigatena visallena sallena (mr)
#. VAR: sekhaṃ → bijjhatu sekhaṃ (bj) | sekkhaṃ (s1-3) | taṃ sekhaṃ (pts1-2, mr)
#. VAR: anupāpuṇātu → anupāpuṇāti (pts1-2, mr)
msgctxt "sn17.7:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kaṃ, bhikkhave, diddhagatena visallena sallena vijjhatu, sekhaṃ "
"appattamānasaṃ lābhasakkārasiloko anupāpuṇātu."
msgstr ""
"Who should be pierced by a poisoned arrow? A trainee who comes into "
"possessions, honor, and popularity before they achieve their heart’s desire."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.7:2.1"
msgid "Sallanti kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasilokassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ."
msgstr "‘Arrow’ is a term for possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "sn17.7:2.2"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.7:2.3"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.7:2.4"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
